des:
"Hi, and greetings to all the listeners we hope to reach over the coming weeks, months, and hopefully years.
MixWorld Radio has been founded by myself DJColinR. Predominantly I'll be playing Soul, Funk, and Disco, the music that has had the most influence on my life. I also have a live show for you to enjoy on a Friday evening UK time, The Friday Funk Fest"
